function arrayUnique(a)
  hash = {}
  out = {}

  for _,v in pairs(a) do
    if (not hash[v]) then
      out[#out+1] = v
      hash[v] = true
    end
  end

  return out
end

function arrayHasValue (a, val)
    for index, value in ipairs(a) do
        if value == val then
            return true
        end
    end

    return false
end

function arraySort(a)
  table.sort(a, function (left, right)
    return left < right
  end)
  return a
end

function arraySortTables(a, prop)
  table.sort(a, function (left, right)
    return left[prop] < right[prop]
  end)
  return a
end

function arrayMerge(a1, a2)
  for _,v in pairs(a2) do
    table.insert(a1, v)
  end
  return arrayUnique(a1);
end

function arrayShuffle(a)
  ret = arrayCopy(a)
  for i = #ret, 2, -1 do
    local j = math.random(i)
    ret[i], ret[j] = ret[j], ret[i]
  end
  return ret
end

function arrayFilter(t, func)
  local out = {}

  for k, v in pairs(t) do
    if func(v, k, t) then table.insert(out,v) end
  end

  return out
end

function arrayCopy(a)
  local copy = {}
  for k,v in pairs(a) do
    copy[k] = v
  end
  return copy
end

function arrayPrint(a)
  print(table.concat(a, ", "))
end

Card = {
  guid = "",
  cost = 0,
  debt = 0,
  potion = 0,
  types = {}
}

function Card:new (o)
  o = o or {}   -- create object if user does not provide one
  setmetatable(o, self)
  self.__index = self
  return o
end

function Card:setup (obj, position, numCards)
  numCards = numCards or 10 -- Default, spawn 10 cards total
  baseClone = obj.clone({ position = position, snap_to_grid = true })
  baseClone.setRotation({0,180,0})
  if (numCards < 2) then return end
  deck = baseClone.clone({ position = { position[1], position[2] + 1, position[3] }})
  for i=1,numCards-2 do
    clone = obj.clone({ position = { position[1], position[2] + 1 + (0.1*i), position[3] }})
    deck = deck.putObject(clone)
  end
  baseClone.putObject(deck)
end

function setup()
  -- Selection
  selectionPool = arrayShuffle(SUPPLY_ELIGIBLE_CARDS)
  selectedCards = {};
  for i=1,10 do
    selectedCard = table.remove(selectionPool, 1)
    table.insert(selectedCards, selectedCard)
  end

  -- Potion Setup
  if (#arrayFilter(selectedCards, function(card) return card.potion > 0 end) > 0) then
    Potion:setup()
  end

  -- Platinum + Colony 11th card pick
  if (#arrayFilter(selectedCards, function(card) return card.guid == Platinum.guid end) > 0) then
    selectedCard = table.remove(selectionPool, 1)
    table.insert(selectedCards, selectedCard)
  end

  -- Placement
  sortedCards = arraySortTables(selectedCards, "cost")
  for index,card in pairs(sortedCards) do
    obj = getObjectFromGUID(card.guid)
    card:setup(obj, supplyPositions[index])
  end

  -- TODO: Trade Route setup
end
